data.description: Welcome to your new home in the charming neighborhood of Chimney Lakes! This spacious 2-story house boasts wood floors, providing a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout. As you enter, you'll appreciate the separate dining room, perfect for hosting family gatherings and special occasions. One of the highlights of this home is the large primary suite conveniently located on the first floor. The primary bathroom features a double vanity, offering plenty of space for your daily routines. The primary closet is a walk-in, providing ample storage for your wardrobe. Upstairs, you'll find two generously sized bedrooms with a convenient Jack and Jill bathroom in between, making it ideal for family members or guests. Ceiling fans are thoughtfully installed throughout the house, ensuring comfort year-round. Cozy up by the wood-burning fireplace in the living area, creating a perfect spot for relaxation on chilly winter evenings. Step outside to the fully fenced backyard, a secure and private space for outdoor activities. The large open front patio is ideal for sipping your morning coffee or enjoying the evening breeze. This property also offers the convenience of an attached two-car garage and a dining nook in the kitchen, in addition to the separate dining room area. Chimney Lakes provides a range of amenities for its residents, including a club pool, tennis courts, basketball courts, a playground, and even a baseball field. Home being sold AS-IS.
